LONG HAND OBJECT CREATION
var person = new Object();

OBJECT LITERAL
  var person = {
      firstname: 'Ejerson',
      lastname: 'Balabas',
      address: {
          street: '111 Main St.',
          city: 'New York',
          state: 'NY'
      }
  };

I CAN CREATE AN OBJECT ANYWHERE THAT I CAN CREATE A VARIABLE
ON THE THE FLY.

function greet(person) {
  console.log('Hi ' + person.firstname);
}

greet(Ejerson); // Hi Ejerson

I CAN PASS AN ANONYMOUS OBJECT INSIDE A FUNCTION INVOCATION
  greet({
      firstname: 'Mary',
      lastname: 'Doe'
  }); // Mary


OBJECT LITERAL SYNTAX IS VERY POWERFUL AND CAN CREATE CLEAN
AND EASY TO WRITE CODES.
